              {
                "type": "link",
                "url": "https://blog.nilenso.com/blog/2023/11/10/spreadsheets-and-small-software"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "\n\nTreesheets is a particularly memorable project in this area: "
              },
              {
                "type": "link",
                "url": "https://strlen.com/treesheets"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "\n\n"
              },
              {
                "type": "link",
                "url": "https://loglo.app"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " experiments with combining a grid with a shared stack per row.\n\n"
